data.description: This is such a charming home.  3 bedroom 2 bath home if perfect for your family. Upper deck is perfect for entertaining and family dinners.  The open floor plan is so cozy with an abundance of natural light.  The Master is located down stairs with plenty of room for an office, sitting room or what ever your heart desires.  Mom and Dad will definately have a nice space for relaxing. Not to mention the large laundry room with storage.
